00:31:27,100 --> 00:31:28,580
"Ayah"

322
00:31:30,580 --> 00:31:31,980
Ya, Ayah.

323
00:31:34,140 --> 00:31:36,300
Maaf.

324
00:31:37,180 --> 00:31:38,700
Begini...

325
00:31:38,820 --> 00:31:42,940
Nama pasien, Kim Jung–hyun,
wanita berusia 29 tahun.

326
00:31:43,060 --> 00:31:47,380
<i>Dia hamil 32 minggu,</i>
