327
00:31:47,500 --> 00:31:50,140
<i>...dia didiagnosis</i>
<i>dengan gliomatosis ganas.</i>

328
00:31:50,620 --> 00:31:57,740
<i>Dia membutuhkan operasi segera,</i>
