446
00:41:33,220 --> 00:41:35,300
Lihatlah sarinya!

447
00:41:38,500 --> 00:41:40,180
Dari mana kau mendapatkan
semua ini?

448
00:41:40,300 --> 00:41:41,700
Di minimarket.

449
00:41:42,500 --> 00:41:44,380
– Di mana dr. Joo?
– Di atas.

450
